Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.66,0:00:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.98,0:01:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:18.36,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7}早上好\N妈妈今天7:15有现场直播\N好紧张哦\N小鸟今天也要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天7点15有现场直播
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.75,0:01:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现场直播？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.46,0:01:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4月24日 星期六 现在是7点15分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 从今晚7点开始播出的「猜谜学园智慧智慧特别篇」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们请来了各位特别嘉宾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟 你在看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.72,0:01:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,紬希和久等了的汉堡肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.53,0:03:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的那份焦焦的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的责任自己担
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味 味增汤怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点煮沸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一边回想猪肉酱汤的做法 一边调了味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,油豆腐好长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊 紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是中奖了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗 还有这种奖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘎哩嘎哩先生毛绒绒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希 你等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你收桌子 紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后的等爸爸回来以后做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有报纸 报纸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上一打开电视节目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈穿着水手服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信 那样太难以置信了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 就算是上电视
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有能做的事和不能做的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我都没穿过水手服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她穿着还挺合适的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈很忙碌就是因为这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然她也不是成了艺人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 早饭做的怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西式炒蛋烧焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 但是 味增汤做出来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加了味增以后 稍微煮了一会儿就煮干了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能再加水稀释
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 你害怕半生不熟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 如果紬希吃坏肚子可就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小紬希 我们玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在做汉堡肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是爸爸的份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是做了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就得做碗 筷子和勺子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦 你用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近我都没玩粘土 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小朋友们 差不多要收拾了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小紬希今天要来我家玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拜托过爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小 小紬希 那个会不会很重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 这粘土是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你 是别人送的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 这家伙拿了别人的粘土
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是哦 是别人給的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这样太不公平了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己独占 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别人给的就是紬希的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不准备还啊 那不就是小偷了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:03.56,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs28\frz3.5\pos(373.438,126.067)}不擅长做菜也没问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:03.56,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs28\frz3.5\pos(410.413,251.044)}简单菜谱3万份以上！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:03.56,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs28\frz3.5\pos(441.925,281.178)}关键词搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:03.56,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs28\frz3.5\pos(701.975,335.4)}汉堡肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬塚老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么好事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 为什么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 我是犬塚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 那我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女儿好像有点纠纷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬塚先生 抱歉把您喊来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 紬希和干雄君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小紬希挠了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希才设有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干雄君推了—把
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后碰到小紬希的手了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是有意的哦 老师都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她就是做了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希 你用手碰到人家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希才没有做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听老师说你又弄哭女孩子了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 才没弄哭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「咚」的一下然后「哧溜」一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她用手「呼嗡」一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到了 我就被挠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始是干雄「咚」的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你得跟人家道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 好好道歉和好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希 干雄君在跟你道歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小紬希 听他说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我回家和她慢慢谈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小紬希拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉哦 下次再一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希 现在只有爸爸在了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粘土是别人给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道哦 紬希不是小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他对你说了讨厌的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去买粘土 还给大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为爸爸也觉得就算是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不想紬希被叫做「小偷」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要做久等了的汉堡肉饼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来她相当失落呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且今天早上和解了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她好像心里还是不痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想做汉堡肉饼让她打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 我们加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是汉堡肉饼的火候很难掌控吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们用煮的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煮？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煮汉堡肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就不会有中间半生不熟的状况了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又能做的好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以接下来 请老师切末
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这个和这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为眼睛可能会出大事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出大事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 痒？疼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之 好好保护眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这眼镜上面很松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 她有点在笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的哎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 切末该怎么切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道能不能参考
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我姑且让她写在「妈妈菜谱」里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:03.67,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(13.2,16.8)}☆洋葱切末\N切成两半\N一开始从旁边切\N然后竖着切\N咕噜一下转过来\N很简单吧\N没切碎的地方\N用菜刀尖端压住细细切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乍一看 完全看不懂写的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我觉得自己好像做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 把剥了皮的洋葱切成两半
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天非常没有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会受伤 你还是别看了比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始 从旁边切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下这部分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备了很多创可贴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后竖着切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咕噜一下转过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从上方切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切成末了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 好像变戏法一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把切成末的洋葱炒至糖稀色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糖稀色是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半透明的淡茶色看上去很好吃的颜色哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心别让它焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你闻 开始有香味飘出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 面包糠用牛奶泡开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:44.10,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs35\pos(20,17.4)}汉堡肉饼材料\N猪肉馅 150克\N牛肉馅 150克\N洋葱 1个\N鸡蛋 半个\N牛奶 两大勺\N盐 半小勺\N胡椒 少许\N橄榄油 一大勺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:44.10,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs35\pos(1077.6,14.2)}酱汁\N大蒜 1份\N盐 半小勺\N胡椒 少许\N月桂树叶 2片\N番茄罐头 1罐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:44.10,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs32\pos(525.6,74.4)\frz354.4}今晚的晚饭菜谱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:44.10,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs32\frz354.4\pos(212,436)}首先来切洋葱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:44.10,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs32\frz354.4\pos(786.4,498.4)}切的时候可能会掉眼泪呢…加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:44.10,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs32\frz354.4\pos(839.2,538.4)}切末的方法写在另一张纸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放的材料比我想象中少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很美味 但基础很简单呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 有人喜欢加入豆腐渣或者豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有人会加猕猴桃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:15:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猕猴桃的成份能让肉变得柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧的松松软软
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和在咕咾肉里加菠萝是一个道理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希 要不要帮帮爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面要把肉捏出形状 你喜欢玩粘土的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希 你要怎样才能打起精神来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 我觉得自己做了坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希不是小偷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也说了爸爸明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样 不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再努力问问 好好问问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是收到了好多粘土 没有还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希是坏孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希不是坏孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸知道紬希是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希又温柔 又听活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会帮忙做家务
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 还有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希给了爸爸好多 好多活力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸最喜欢紬希了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来做汉堡肉饼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 把这揉啊揉啊揉出来的肉馅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样一边调整形状
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边把空气拍出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做的很棒哦 紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始煎了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反面…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待会儿还要煮 只要有煎过的颜色就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盛出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酱汁就简单地用番茄罐头做酱底
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加入英国辣酱油和番茄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后加入固体白汤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在这时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样煮透就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我们来收尾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收尾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成 成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在至今的料理中 外表最让人垂涎欲滴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了 紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希 头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不管紬希是怎样的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸都最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松松软软的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们太厉害了 今天也做的很成功
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了小紬希本来想用黏土做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的生礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸今天过生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是4和2和5的日子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只能做成小小的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会送你粘土汉堡肉饼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 今天是你的生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:40.67,Top,,0,0,0,,紬希 好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:42.63,Top,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我 只能做这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.43,0:21:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这拌上了稠稠的蛋液 恐怕是最好吃的部分…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送给你 这是礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没事 不需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 请您别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.61,0:21:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
